#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Mängureeglid, strateegia ja nõuanded"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Reeglid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot be stopped once they leave a planet."
msgstr "Teele saadetud laevu ei saa enam peatada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot attack other ships in midair."
msgstr "Laevad ei saa rünnata teisi laevu väljaspool planeete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships can be stored at planets for later use."
msgstr "Laevad võib jätta planeedile seisma hilisemaks kasutamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "A planet cannot be given away."
msgstr "Planeeti ei saa niisama loovutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A player can skip a turn by pressing <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton> without "
"launching any ships."
msgstr ""
"Mängija võib käigu vahele jätta, klõpsates nupule <guibutton>Käigu lõpp</"
"guibutton> ilma laevu välja saatmata."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strateegia ja nõuanded"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game is all about ship production. Try to get as many planets as "
"possible as fast as you can in order to build more ships than any of your "
"opponents."
msgstr ""
"Mängu tuumaks on laevade tootmine. Ürita hõivata nii kiiresti kui võimalik "
"nii palju planeete kui võimalik, et ehitada rohkem laevu kui ükski sinu "
"vastane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not attack a planet with less than 10 ships, unless you can conquer it."
msgstr ""
"Ära ründa planeeti vähem kui 10 laevaga, kui sa just ei ole kindel, et "
"suudad ka nii selle vallutada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attack neutral planets before other players' planets."
msgstr ""
"Ründa kõigepealt neutraalseid planeete, alles siis vastasmängijate omi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split your ship storages across several planets."
msgstr "Jaga oma laevavarud mitme planeedi vahel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plan your attacks in advance."
msgstr "Kavanda oma rünnakuid ette."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the ruler to find out the distance between planets."
msgstr "Kasuta mõõdikut planeetide vahemaa tuvastamiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the information window to get information on planets before an attack."
msgstr ""
"Hangi teabeaknast kasulikku teavet planeedi kohta enne selle ründamist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this information is available to you, it is preferable to attack a planet "
"with a low kill ratio from a planet with a high one."
msgstr ""
"Kui vastav teave on saadaval, tasub eelistada väikese tapatõhususega "
"planeetide ründamist suure tapatõhususega planeetide ründamisele."

