#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I redirect ships once they have left a planet?"
msgstr "Kas laevu saab pärast väljasaatmist mujale ümber suunata?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, once ships leave a planet, they cannot be stopped or redirected."
msgstr ""
"Ei. Kui laevad on planeedilt lahkunud, ei saa neid enam peatada ega ümber "
"suunata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do the different colors and shapes of planets mean anything?"
msgstr "Kas planeetide eri värvidel ja kujul on mingi tähendus?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, they are random."
msgstr "Ei, need on juhuslikud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I know where my ships are?"
msgstr "Kuidas ma teada saan, kus on mu laevad?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>Show Standings</guibutton>. It will give you information "
"about fleets currently in flight."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa <guibutton>Näita seisu</guibutton>, mis näitab, kus asuvad parajasti "
"teel laevastikud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have lost all my planets, but I am still in the game, why?"
msgstr "Ma kaotasin kõik planeedid, aga olen ikka mängus. Miks?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "You have not lost the game until you have lost all your ships."
msgstr "Sa kaotad mängu alles siis, kui kaotad kõik oma laevad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I store ships on a planet for later use?"
msgstr "Kas laevu saab jätta planeedile hilisemaks kasutamiseks?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, you should however store them on multiple planets to be able to send "
"them to nearby planets."
msgstr ""
"Jah ja seda peakski tegema, kusjuures mõtet on paigutada laevu mitmele "
"planeedile, et saata nad sealt teistele lähedal asuvatele planeetidele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is it possible to change the theme?"
msgstr "Kas teemat saab vahetada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, that is not possible at the moment."
msgstr "Ei, see ei ole veel võimalik."

